-- Merkel, Sarkozy Likely to Discuss Exchange Rates, Commodities at Meeting
-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 2010-10-15T09:42:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/merkel-sarkozy-likely-to-discuss-exchange-rates-commodities-at-meeting.html
Chancellor Angela Merkel and French
President Nicolas Sarkozy will likely discuss global currency
fluctuations and commodities prices when they meet next week in
France, German government spokesman Steffen Seibert said today
in Berlin. Russian President Dmitry Medvedev will also attend
the summit meeting.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick Donahue at 
 pdonahue1@bloomberg.net  